sql:
SELECT book_id, MAX(edition_date) AS latest_edition_date
FROM book_editions
GROUP BY book_id;

external_knowledge:
- The term 'best-selling books' refers to books with high total sales; 
- Total sales are calculated by multiplying the quantity of books sold by the price at which they were sold; 
- Average customer ratings are calculated by taking the average of all ratings given by reviewers, with ratings ranging from 1 to 5.
